奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 推出定制 T 恤，支持禁止战利品狩猎，他称这种行为“完全疯狂” https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-unveils-custom-t-shirt-in-support-of-banning-tropy-hunting-which-he-calls-totally-crazy-3814032？ utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=ozzy-osbourne-unveils-custom-T-shirt-in-support-of-banning-troy-hunting-which-he-calls-totally-crazyDaniel Peters Tue, 19 Nov 2024 14:19:29 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3814032 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2011 年 4 月 25 日，奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 在纽约参观 2011 年翠贝卡电影节肖像工作室。 （拉里·布萨卡/盖蒂图片社为翠贝卡电影节拍摄）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “你必须通过吠叫来杀死一只无辜的动物，然后拍下自己笑着的照片”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-unveils-custom-t-shirt-in-support-of-banning-trophy-hunting-which-he-calls-totally-crazy-3814032">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 推出定制 T 恤，支持禁止战利品狩猎，他称这种行为“完全疯狂”，</a>这篇文章首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="2011 年 4 月 25 日，奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 在纽约参观 2011 年翠贝卡电影节肖像工作室。 （拉里·布萨卡/盖蒂图片社为翠贝卡电影节拍摄）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/Ozzy-Osbourne-posing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ozzy-osbourne">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne)</a>推出了一款他设计的 T 恤，以支持一项旨在禁止战利品狩猎的运动，他称这种爱好“完全疯狂”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/ozzy-osbourne-tour-retirement-black-sabbath-3390656">奥兹·奥斯本（Ozzy Osbourne）：无与伦比的摇滚表演者</a></strong></li></ul><p>英国禁止奖杯狩猎组织昨天（11 月 18 日）发布了一段视频剪辑，视频中奥斯本和他的妻子莎伦穿着他定制的 T 恤，上面写着“奥兹说‘禁止奖杯狩猎！’”。</p><p> “来吧，你们。我们所做的就是谈论它，”剪辑中莎伦热情地说。 “让我们把它完成吧！”</p><p>在通过<a href="https://consequence.net/2024/11/ozzy-osbourne-t-shirt-ban-trophy-hunting/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Consequence</em></a>发布的新闻声明中，奥兹称战利品猎人“完全疯狂”。</p><p> “你必须通过吠叫来杀死一只无辜的动物，然后拍下自己大笑的照片。”该 T 恤的所有收益将捐献给英国禁止奖杯狩猎组织 (Ban Trophy Hunting UK)。 <a href="https://campaigntobantrophyhuntingstore.com/product/lion-by-ozzy-osbourne-t-shirt/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>购买。 </p><p><iframe title="奥兹和莎朗·奥斯本：让我们禁止奖杯狩猎吧！" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ZpMsTm37XAU?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>他继续说道：“我们都必须尽自己的一份力量。我喜欢设计东西，所以我为禁止狩猎战利品活动设计了一件 T 恤。政府表示将禁止狩猎战利品，所以继续吧！告诉你的国会议员你希望立即禁止它！为自己买一件 Ozzy T 恤作为圣诞节礼物，帮助拯救动物！”</p><p>莎伦补充说，他们希望“每个人都买这件 T 恤，并帮助筹集资金来对抗这些可怕的人。”</p><p> “我想不出还有什么比仅仅为了取乐而杀死一只动物，然后把它的头放在你的客厅里更令人作呕的了。老实说，我以为那些日子已经过去了。让我们消灭战利品狩猎，而不是野生动物。”她还透露，一小批由奥兹和莎伦亲自签名的 T 恤也将被拍卖。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/heres-what-ozzy-osbourne-had-to-say-during-rock-and-roll-hall-of-fame-induction-speech-3804374">奥兹入选摇滚名人堂，</a>以表彰他的独奏生涯，此前他曾于 2006 年作为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/black-sabbath">黑色安息日</a>乐队成员进入。 </p><figure id="attachment_3804384" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3804384" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3804384" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Ozzy-Osbourne-is-inducted-into-the-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame.-CREDIT_-Kevin-Mazur_Getty-Images-for-The-Rock-and-Roll-Hall-of-Fame-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3804384" class="wp-caption-text">奥兹·奥斯本入选摇滚名人堂。图片来源：Kevin Mazur/Getty Images 摇滚名人堂</figcaption></figure><p>他还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-would-jump-at-the-chance-to-play-final-black-sabbath-show-with-bill-ward-its-unfinished-3757022">继续与黑色安息日最后一次重聚的传言联系在一起</a>， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/bill-ward-responds-to-talk-of-black-sabbath-reunion-3778320">包括鼓手比尔·沃德在内的</a>所有四名成员似乎都暂时加入了乐队。</p><p>这位歌手此前曾表示，他将“抓住机会”与沃德一起演出最后一场黑色安息日演出。奥兹曾处理过各种健康问题，例如在 2020 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-living-with-parkinsons-disease-makes-him-feel-like-hes-walking-around-in-lead-boots-3301202">被诊断出患有帕金森氏症</a>，并在去年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-opens-up-about-slow-recovery-after-final-spinal-surgery-3568962">接受了脊柱手术</a>。</p><p>今年年初，莎朗透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-planning-two-more-shows-to-say-goodbye-before-he-quits-touring-3575657">在他完全退出现场表演之前，他们计划“再举办两场告别演出”</a> 。</p><p>据报道，她暗示黑暗王子将在他的家乡伯明翰的维拉公园足球场举办这两场告别音乐会。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-announces-retirement-from-touring-and-cancels-all-remaining-shows-3390301">奥斯本此前于去年二月宣布退出巡演</a>，并取消了原定的欧洲和英国巡演日期。然而，当月晚些时候， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-says-he-would-tour-again-weeks-after-announcing-his-retirement-3406010">他表示希望在未来的某个时候重返舞台</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ozzy-osbourne-unveils-custom-t-shirt-in-support-of-banning-trophy-hunting-which-he-calls-totally-crazy-3814032">奥兹·奥斯本 (Ozzy Osbourne) 推出定制 T 恤，支持禁止战利品狩猎，他称之为“完全疯狂”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
